com.facebook.buck.util

Class DuplicatingConsole

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.util.Console
      • com.facebook.buck.util.DuplicatingConsole

  • public class DuplicatingConsole
extends Console
    Manages a Duplicate Console so that console actions can be replicated across to another console.

    Example use case is to duplicate a console that writes to system stdout/stderr to a Log file.
